</p></div>\n\";i:3;s:547:\"\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\" style=\"position:relative;\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre class=\"bash\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#91;</span>root<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">@</span>192 ~<span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#93;</span><span style=\"color: #666666; font-style: italic;\">#tar xvf mysql-5.7.17.tar.gz -C /usr/local/</span></pre></td></tr></table><p class=\"theCode\" style=\"display:none;\">[root@192 ~]#tar xvf mysql-5.7.17.tar.gz -C /usr/local/</p></div>\n\";i:4;s:1153:\"\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\" style=\"position:relative;\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre class=\"bash\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#91;</span>root<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">@</span>192 ~<span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#93;</span><span style=\"color: #666666; font-style: italic;\">#yum install -y ncurses-devel</span>\n&nbsp;\n<span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#91;</span>root<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">@</span>192 ~<span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#93;</span><span style=\"color: #666666; font-style: italic;\">#yum install -y bison</span>\n&nbsp;\n<span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#91;</span>root<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">@</span>192 ~<span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">&#93;</span><span style=\"color: #666666; font-style: italic;\">#yum install -y gcc gcc-c++</span></pre></td></tr></table><p class=\"theCode\" style=\"display:none;\">[root@192 ~]#yum install -y ncurses-devel\r\n\r\n[root@192 ~]#yum install -y bison\r\n\r\n[root@192 ~]#yum install -y gcc gcc-c++</p></div>\n\";i:5;s:3309:\"\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\" style=\"position:relative;\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre class=\"bash\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #7a08