;\">-P</span> <span style=\"color: #007800;\">$Dpath</span> http:<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">//</span>mirrors.sohu.com<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>mysql<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>MySQL-<span style=\"color: #000000;\">5.7</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>mysql-5.7.17-linux-glibc2.5-x86_64.tar.gz\n    <span style=\"color: #c20cb9; font-weight: bold;\">wget</span> <span style=\"color: #660033;\">-P</span> <span style=\"color: #007800;\">$Dpath</span> <span style=\"color: #660033;\">--no-check-certificate</span> <span style=\"color: #660033;\">--no-cookie</span> <span style=\"color: #660033;\">--header</span> <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&quot;Cookie: oraclelicense=accept-securebackup-cookie;&quot;</span> http:<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">//</span>download.oracle.com<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>otn-pub<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>java<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>jdk<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>8u152-b16<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>aa0333dd3019491ca4f6ddbe78cdb6d0<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">/</span>jdk-8u152-linux-x64.tar.gz\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">else</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #7a0874; font-weight: bold;\">echo</span> <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">\'INVALID ENTRY\'</span>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">fi</span></pre></td></tr></table><p class=\"theCode\" style=\"display:none;\">#/bin/bash\r\n#\r\n#wang_chongsheng@163.com\r\n##2017-10-30\r\n##JDK&amp;&amp;MySQL下载\r\nDpath=\'/opt/install/src\'\r\n\r\necho 应用编号：\r\necho 1.jdk-8u152-linux-x64.tar.gz\r\necho 2.mysql-5.7.17-linux-glibc2.5-x86_64.tar.gz\r\necho 3.jdk and MySQL\r\necho \r\nread -p &quot;input a val:&quot; val\r\nif [ $val == 1 ]; then\r\n    wget -P $Dpath --no-check-certificate --no-cookie --header &quot;Cookie: oraclelicense=accept-securebackup-cookie;&quot; http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/8u152-b16/aa0333dd3019491ca4f6ddbe78cdb6d0/jdk-8u152-linux-x64.tar.gz\r\nelif [ $val == 2 ]; then\r\n    wget -P $Dpath http://mirrors.sohu.com/mysql/MySQL-5.7/mysql-5.7.17-linux-glibc2.5-x86_64.tar.gz\r\nelif [ $val == 3 ]; then\r\n    wget -P $Dpath http://mirrors.sohu.com/mysql/MySQL-5.7/mysql-5.7.17-linux-glibc2.5-x86_64.tar.gz\r\n    wget -P $Dpath --no-check-certificate --no-cookie --header &quot;Cookie: oraclelicense=accept-securebackup-cookie;&quot; http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/8u152-b16/aa0333dd3019491ca4f6ddbe78cdb6d0/jdk-8u152-linux-x64.tar.gz\r\nelse\r\n    echo \'INVALID ENTRY\'\r\nfi</p></div>\n\";}');
